Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on June 24, 2026, the following bill was signed into law:
H.B. NO. 2050, H.D. 1, S.D. 1, RELATING TO PARTIAL PUBLIC FINANCING OF
C.D. 1 ELECTIONS.
